pokedexEntries.red: Very smart and very vengeful. Grabbing one of its many tails could result in a 1000-year curse.
pokedexEntries.blue: Very smart and very vengeful. Grabbing one of its many tails could result in a 1000-year curse.
pokedexEntries.yellow: According to an enduring legend, 9 noble saints were united and reincarnated as this Pokémon.
pokedexEntries.gold: Some legends claim that each of its nine tails has its own unique type of special mystic power.
pokedexEntries.silver: Its nine beautiful tails are filled with a wondrous energy that could keep it alive for 1,000 years.
pokedexEntries.crystal: It is said to live a thousand years, and each of its tails is loaded with supernatural powers.
pokedexEntries.ruby: Ninetales casts a sinister light from its bright red eyes to gain total control over its foe's mind. This Pokémon is said to live for a thousand years.
pokedexEntries.sapphire: Legend has it that Ninetales came into being when nine wizards possessing sacred powers merged into one. This Pokémon is highly intelligent - it can understand human speech.
pokedexEntries.emerald: It has long been said that each of the nine tails embody an enchanted power. A long-lived Ninetales will have fur that shines like gold.
pokedexEntries.fireRed: It has nine long tails and fur that gleams gold. It is said to live for 1,000 years.
pokedexEntries.leafGreen: Very smart and very vengeful. Grabbing one of its many tails could result in a 1,000-year curse.
pokedexEntries.diamond: Its nine tails are said to be imbued with a mystic power. It can live for a thousand years.
pokedexEntries.pearl: Its nine tails are said to be imbued with a mystic power. It can live for a thousand years.
pokedexEntries.platinum: Its nine tails are said to be imbued with a mystic power. It can live for a thousand years.
pokedexEntries.heartGold: Some legends claim that each of its nine tails has its own unique type of special mystic power.
pokedexEntries.soulSilver: Its nine beautiful tails are filled with a wondrous energy that could keep it alive for 1,000 years.
pokedexEntries.black: Its nine tails are said to be imbued with a mystic power. It can live for a thousand years.
pokedexEntries.white: Its nine tails are said to be imbued with a mystic power. It can live for a thousand years.
pokedexEntries.black2: Each of its nine tails is imbued with supernatural power, and it can live for a thousand years.
pokedexEntries.white2: Each of its nine tails is imbued with supernatural power, and it can live for a thousand years.
pokedexEntries.x: It has nine long tails and fur that gleams gold. It is said to live for 1,000 years.
pokedexEntries.y: Very smart and very vengeful. Grabbing one of its many tails could result in a 1,000 year curse.
pokedexEntries.omegaRuby: Ninetales casts a sinister light from its bright red eyes to gain total control over its foe's mind. This Pokémon is said to live for one thousand years.
pokedexEntries.alphaSapphire: Legend has it that Ninetales came into being when nine wizards possessing sacred powers merged into one. This Pokémon is highly intelligent—it can understand human speech.
pokedexEntries.sun: Legend has it that this mystical Pokémon was formed when nine saints coalesced into one.
pokedexEntries.moon: Said to live for a thousand years, this Pokémon uses its supernatural abilities to manipulate fire. It can burn its prey to a crisp as it pleases.
pokedexEntries.ultraSun: It is vindictive and relentless by nature. Those who cross it even once will be cursed for a thousand years, along with their descendants.
pokedexEntries.ultraMoon: The flickering flames it spews from its mouth leave its opponents hypnotized. Then, this extremely intelligent Pokémon attacks.
